org.jboss.windup.graph

Annotation Type Indexed


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Indexed
    Designates that a Framed method annotated with Property should be indexed by the underlying database implementation. This is used as a runtime performance enhancement, but comes at the cost of using additional storage space (and potentially memory.)

    Note: Only one property in any getter/setter pair need be annotated with Indexed. Multiple annotations will have no effect.

    Author:
    Lincoln Baxter, III
